  <summary date="2021-06-16T16:37:58Z" status="Passed Senate">School-Based Allergies and Asthma Management Program Act

This bill establishes preferences for grants under the children's asthma treatment program for states that require schools to establish allergy and asthma management programs that include individual action plans for students diagnosed with allergies or asthma.</summary>
